Special lightweight, fully working version of Windows XP, which comes as to set a fast workstation, and as a gaming machine.

Version 1.0.0 [testing]

The advantages compared with the normal version of Windows:

- Windows will license! Will be authenticated on the website of Microsoft
- Integrated Service pack 3, including all critical updates and patches in 2008 (August)!
- Interface changed to the maximum extent possible appearance of Windows Vista
- Super fast and quiet installation
- Turn off any unnecessary services (processes will be minimum)
- Delete unnecessary driver, certificates, etc.
- Version Russian corporate, does not require any activation!
- Update for DirectX 9.0c August 2008, except for the MDX
- It integrates Internet Explorer 7, Windows Media Player 11 Russian version
- Added many small interesting fich
- Vinda will fly even in the weakest machines!
